Clark Copy InternationalCorp said it bought a Norwegian drafting machines company forthree mln U.S. dlrs.    Clark Copy said its majority-owned Norwegian subsidiary,Interactive Computer Aids Co of Norway, purchased KongsbergDrafting Systems, a division of Norwegian state-owned KongsbergVappenfabrikk.    Kongsberg Drafting's annual worldwide sales are about 15mln dlrs, Clark Copy said. Reuter&#3;